codebookDescription: 22. HIV can be transmitted by sharing a meal with an infected person

codebookDescription: 23. It is possible for a healthy-looking person to have HIV

label: PrEP knowledge

label: All individuals found to be HIV negative are fit to use PrEP
codebookDescription: 32. All individuals found to be HIV negative are fit to use PrEP

label: PrEP is effective if you take it on a one-off basis (like a morning after pill)
codebookDescription: 33. PrEP is effective if you take it on a one-off basis (like a morning after pill)

label: Once one is initiated on PrEP it is to be taken for life
codebookDescription: 34. Once one is initiated on PrEP it is to be taken for life

codebookDescription: 35. PrEP is safe for women during pregnancy and breastfeeding
